languages.text: [draft]Enemies under the effect of the Psyker's {g|Encyclopedia:PsykerPowersGlossary}psychic powers{/g} suffer +10% {g|Encyclopedia:DamageGlossary}damage{/g} from the Psyker's allies under the effect of the Psyker's {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}abilities{/g} from doctrines or psychic powers. This {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} increases to +20% if an ally is under the effect of both the Psyker's psychic power and the Psyker's ability from a {g|Encyclopedia:Career}doctrine{/g}.

traits.locale_text: [draft]Enemies under the effect of the Psyker's psychic powers suffer +10% damage from the Psyker's allies under the effect of the Psyker's abilities from doctrines or psychic powers. This bonus increases to +20% if an ally is under the effect of both the Psyker's psychic power and the Psyker's ability from a doctrine.
